통계학 개론's summary

5. estimate 추정
   to estimate from the sample data to the parameter 
  # estimator 추정량
   the statistic in a estimating
  
  # testing 검정
   to test the validity of a claim of the population by samples
   
   # point estimate 점 추정
    it suggests only a value for a parameter
   
   # interval estimate 구간 추정
    it suggests a interval or a range. it also brings you the parameter's estimate value and the precision(정확도). 
    
   # confidence interval
